author: thedavid
title: Cool keychain
review:
Lots of keychains are made. But a few are very original. this is a keychain whitch is a mummy! I love the theme Egypt, so I like it, but not every person is a fan! This is just something for LEGO. a mummie has bin made many times. in the Adventurers, Studios...

But this is one of the best.

 

Conclusion:

Great keychain. But if you aren't lego-fan, it's not something for you
